==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: break-in
<hw>break-in</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an act of trespassing into a closed
structure such as a house or place of business for an unlawful purpose,
usually as part of a burglary.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> housebreaking, breaking and entering.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>breaking</ent>⟦br⟧
